                                ReactJS.
                            </p>
                            <div>
                                <a href="/" class="home-banner-btn">Đăng ký ngay</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div><img class="d-block w-100"
                                src="https://files.fullstack.edu.vn/f8-prod/banners/Banner_web_ReactJS.png"
